    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>The flat bands above the uppermost moldings or cymas of cornices, or the small bands above and below the scotia of an Attic base.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
